{"tid":2090942,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有人很煩惱 - 李純恩","createTime":"2020-07-02T12:11:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-02T12:22:58.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4c8f579679ccb03d309c014d8fcca96cd694ae76","tid":2090942,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T12:11:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%B4%94%E6%81%A9/daily/article/20200702/20947723/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25B4%2594%25E6%2581%25A9%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200702%2F20947723%2F&d=oBn6KkEvnt0QU92xe9ZG8Bdm8TOyDCEw47gAfDhO9KY%3D&h=091c200a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25B4%2594%25E6%2581%25A9%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200702%2F20947723%2F&h=4c4472cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%B4%94%E6%81%A9/daily/article/20200702/20947723/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n有人很煩惱 - 李純恩<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200702/large/1593584897_6321.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200702%2Flarge%2F1593584897_6321.jpg&h=2928bf50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n李純恩拍攝<br />\n<br />\n朋友約喝茶聊天，<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n便成天大的事了。<br />\n<br />\n我在一<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n及得罪他。<br />\n<br />\n記得六年前初學畫時，買了一本《芥子園圖譜》臨摹，一天照畫譜畫了一塊石頭，自覺十分相似，見旁邊有空位，便又加了一個紅袍老頭。紅袍老頭畫得極小，相襯之下，那塊普通的石頭就像一座小山一般大了。世界許多事物的大小，其實都是心中一個比例，你把它想大了，它就大，你把它想小了，它就小。一塊石頭你把它想大了，它就如一座山，可以把心堵住，反之，不以為意，那不過是路邊一塊普通石頭。心境如此，眼界也一樣，若是一葉障目，那片葉子就是全世界，把它從眼前拉開，才真正看得到大世界。<br />\n<br />\n遇到心煩的朋友，這種話也只能點到即止，明不明白，就要看各人造化，有的人心頭眼前總是被石頭葉子堵着，真心一片不捨煩惱，那就由得他沉浸下去，免得那煩惱解決了令他悵然若失。雖然沒有人會覺得煩惱有趣，但有的人不煩惱又好像人生沒了情趣，那就隨便他好了。 <br />\n<br />\n李純恩<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"},{"pid":"1d319e363b74c80335e0dd9b72d44b97b82856e7","tid":2090942,"uid":165749,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T12:22:58.000Z","msg":"講得好，你看見怎麼，是你決定的<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}